  "texts": [
    "[54] and UNER [44], datasets are used for performance evaluation using word-level, language-dependent and, language-independent features.",
    "Their DNN model outperforms traditional approaches on all three corpora with F-scores of 81.1%, 79.9%, and 63.21% respectively.",
    "Authors in [55, 56] apply the DL approaches on the MKPUCIT dataset [30].",
    "Three pre-trained embeddings i.e., word2vec, Glove, and FastText are generated and input to BiLSTM.",
    "The output of BiLSTM is passed to the self-attention layer and then the dense layer."
